Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1

(1 comment)

I assume this is needed because glance_store has some requirements to configure swift, hence my comment.

I also noticed is that both, glance-api.conf and glance-registry.conf, require configs to be generated for a namespace `glance.store`. However, there's no namespace `glance.store` but `glance_store`. Should this be changed?

One more thing, glance-registry.conf shouldn't require `glance_store`.

The above could be done in follow-up patches, though.
